lyrics:
[Verse]
In the city lights, we're lost tonight
Our hearts collide, we're feeling so alive
Guitars screaming, drums beating in our souls
Rocking together, our love story unfolds

[Chorus]
Falling to the rhythm, our hearts entwined
Love echoes through the melodies we find
We're dancing to the music 'til the break of dawn
Rocking love, forever it carries us on
